{"title":"归来的心","authors":["培勋"],"dates":[{"year":1987,"month":11,"day":19}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"归来的心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"培勋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怀揣父老滔滔的宿愿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“希望号”渐渐靠岸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你尽管踏上太阳的乐土"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也忍不住游子的悲酸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖先留下的肤色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"处处奔涌着炽热的情感"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听一听扑来的乡音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"催促你走向熟悉的摇篮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在长城边"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你抹干民族的创痕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炎黄的血脉从这里相连"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"饮一口黄河乳汁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骨肉终于团圆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也许阿里山的姑娘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与日月潭同样芳秀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拂去流了三十年的苦泪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们已经找到完整的语言"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}